snippet.title: One Box One Goal | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
One Box One Goal is a challenging 3D platform puzzle game that takes homage by the iconic "Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy." Take control of a character trapped inside a box, armed only with a trusty hammer and reach the end.

Coming late 2024. (Date may be subject to change).

Wishlist One Box One Goal on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2541550/One_Box_One_Goal/

Discord Server: https://discord.gg/Tb7k3YfR9B
